description:
A Map by Hive

The locations and histories of towns named after nations (and towns with the same names as nations).  This is an open map, so if you have the scoop on a town that fit this map, feel free to add it in.

While looking around for a map icon that would make sense for this map, i stumbled upon a pretty inspiring essay on the chnaging role of globalization as it's network becomes more and more visible.
Here is a short quote from the intro ... 
&amp;quot;How did the globalizing world of the 1990s become visible as a unified political-economic system? And what happens, when a world becomes visible?&amp;quot;
